{"tid":1300410,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[明日香港]  回帶 衝紅燈被人臉識別捉到正　螢幕即登個人資料　安徽大媽傻眼一分鐘","createTime":"2019-07-09T11:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T01:44:26.000Z","uid":18485,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0a64f0da5db88f1176ee51c4c099f10a85f9610e","tid":1300410,"uid":18485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:03:38.000Z","msg":"安徽界首市上月28日啟用「行人闖紅燈抓拍系統」，一名大媽衝紅燈過馬路時，剛好被這系統發現了，並將她的資料及闖紅燈過程在附近電子螢幕上發布，大媽一抬頭就發現螢幕上有自己的樣子，一時反應不過來，呆呆地站在原地看了近一分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方指，「機器在測試過程中，老太太剛好闖紅燈經過斑馬線，被這個系統抓拍，當時老太太看了有一分鐘左右，她可能覺得很奇怪，『怎麼我就出現在屏幕上了』，之後我們會教育她」。警方指出，這個系統是為了加強市區道路秩序管理，未來這個系統抓到的違規民眾的資料亦會在微博上公開，加強阻嚇作用。<br />\n<br />\n明日香港<br />\n共享大湾区荣耀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2866499/org/ecf492773c2b42e732ba95fd7970604e.jpg/hKL1fTue8Yq1t7kWNG_cmPG93LJKuQU1a7VsOmu1bDo?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2866499%2Forg%2Fecf492773c2b42e732ba95fd7970604e.jpg%2FhKL1fTue8Yq1t7kWNG_cmPG93LJKuQU1a7VsOmu1bDo%3Fv%3Dw640&h=b14475e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2866503/org/369a0f5a9e3fa441b7e71fa342c009cb.jpg/qbLaTfMLQBCDK13IQvsaIaPATWlqXPWG2smB-NrJgfg?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2866503%2Forg%2F369a0f5a9e3fa441b7e71fa342c009cb.jpg%2FqbLaTfMLQBCDK13IQvsaIaPATWlqXPWG2smB-NrJgfg%3Fv%3Dw640&h=95e94af8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2866502/org/a700acc5241cd74e974f732443324a74.jpg/Fni5SPK58IAj-cIBmq6ZiRU13sVZ6PNzlSCZC5UgmQs?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2866502%2Forg%2Fa700acc5241cd74e974f732443324a74.jpg%2FFni5SPK58IAj-cIBmq6ZiRU13sVZ6PNzlSCZC5UgmQs%3Fv%3Dw640&h=d8939c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/image